{"id":4995,"date":"2020-07-03T11:14:53","date_gmt":"2020-07-03T04:14:53","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/?post_type=product&#038;p=4995"},"modified":"2023-03-31T10:33:29","modified_gmt":"2023-03-31T03:33:29","slug":"rem-cuon-chong-nang-100-tai-cau-giay-ha-noi","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-100-tai-cau-giay-ha-noi","title":{"rendered":"R\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng 100% t\u1ea1i C\u1ea7u Gi\u1ea5y, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i"},"content":{"rendered":"<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; color: #000080;\"><strong>R\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng 100% t\u1ea1i C\u1ea7u Gi\u1ea5y, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong> <\/span><\/h2>\n<p><em><strong>R\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng t\u1ea1i C\u1ea7u Gi\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh thi c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m Anh Ng\u1eef OCEN EDU t\u1ea1i C\u1ea7u Gi\u1ea5y H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. V\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u00f4 c\u1eeda k\u00ednh c\u1ee7a tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc th\u00ec r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng 100% l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn. N\u00f3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u01a1n, m\u00e1t m\u1ebb h\u01a1n v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y n\u00f3ng b\u1ee9c. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t v\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n b\u1ee5i, d\u1ec5 v\u1ec7 sinh lau ch\u00f9i\u00a0<\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; color: #000080;\"><strong>1.\u00a0 R\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng l\u00e0 g\u00ec? C\u1ea5u t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u1ec1 r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; color: #000080;\"><strong>1.1 R\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><strong>R\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/strong> l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m c\u1eeda th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u\u00a0l\u00e0\u00a0c\u00e1c t\u1ea5m v\u1ea3i c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1eafn s\u00e1ng ho\u1eb7c xuy\u00ean s\u00e1ng. T\u1ea5m v\u1ea3i\u00a0r\u00e8m\u00a0n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u00a0cu\u1ed1n\u00a0quanh m\u1ed9t tr\u1ee5c b\u1eb1ng nh\u00f4m m\u1eb7t c\u1eaft tr\u00f2n, khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd k\u00e9o t\u1ea5m v\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi khi kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u1eefa th\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\u00a0cu\u1ed9n l\u00ean t\u00f9y \u00fd. Vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea3 ho\u1eb7c k\u00e9o r\u00e8m l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y s\u00e1ng th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng qua m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 r\u00f2ng r\u1ecdc d\u00e2y k\u00e9o ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u01a1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n d\u00f9ng s\u1ee9c k\u00e9o tay.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4996\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4996\" style=\"width: 1227px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-4996 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1227\" height=\"920\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay.jpg 1227w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-510x382.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1227px) 100vw, 1227px\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4996\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng t\u1ea1i ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdc<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4997\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4997\" style=\"width: 1227px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-4997 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1227\" height=\"920\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-1.jpg 1227w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-1-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-1-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-1-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-1-510x382.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1227px) 100vw, 1227px\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4997\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng 100% m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng ng\u00e0 gi\u00fap tr\u00e1nh n\u1eafng n\u00f3ng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; color: #000080;\"><strong>1.2.\u00a0C\u1ea5u t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u1ec1 r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>V\u1ec1 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n c\u1ea5u t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng, c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n bao g\u1ed3m: tr\u1ee5c cu\u1ed1n r\u00e8m b\u1eb1ng kim lo\u1ea1i, m\u00e0nh r\u00e8m l\u00e0m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i kh\u00e1c nhau, b\u00e1nh chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng, gi\u00e1 treo, c\u00e1c ch\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb,\u2026 M\u1ed7i lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1edbi m\u1eabu m\u00e3, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c nhau, tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n th\u00ec c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec1u bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea5u t\u1ea1o nh\u01b0 v\u1eeba n\u00eau.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4891\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4891\" style=\"width: 512px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-4891 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/cau-tao-rem-cuon-chong-nang-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"512\" height=\"448\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/cau-tao-rem-cuon-chong-nang-1.jpg 512w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/cau-tao-rem-cuon-chong-nang-1-457x400.jpg 457w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/cau-tao-rem-cuon-chong-nang-1-510x446.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4891\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">c\u1ea5u t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4998\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4998\" style=\"width: 1292px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-4998 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1292\" height=\"969\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-2.jpg 1292w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-2-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-