ng-nang-tai-cau-giay-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1227\" height=\"920\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-4.jpg 1227w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-4-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-4-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-4-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-4-510x382.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1227px) 100vw, 1227px\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-5000\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi kh\u00f4ng gian<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif;\">2. \u01afu nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng t\u1ea1i C\u1ea7u Gi\u1ea5y<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>R\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ng\u00e0y nay \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng, do lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m c\u1eeda n\u00e0y mang m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o, g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u0111em l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. R\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n r\u1ea5t thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00e9o l\u00ean xu\u1ed1ng g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng v\u00e0 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng gian l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t.<\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\">2.1.R\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i:<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng\u00a0c\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u00a0ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng, nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng ho\u1eb7c khu v\u1ef1c c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng, n\u1eafng n\u00f3ng. R\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n ho\u00e0n to\u1ea3n \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng b\u00ean ngo\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfu v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng, c\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 tia UV c\u00f3 h\u1ea1i cho s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng:<br \/>\n&#8211; Ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng, c\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng 100%, c\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t l\u00e0m m\u00e1t cho c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng.<br \/>\n&#8211; Khi k\u00e9o r\u00e8m xu\u1ed1ng mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ri\u00eang t\u01b0 v\u00e0 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i.<br \/>\n&#8211; L\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfm di\u1ec7n t\u00edch.<\/p>\n<p>Nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng:<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Trong khi k\u00e9o r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n l\u00ean xu\u1ed1ng g\u00e2y cho v\u1ea3i r\u00e8m r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb b\u00e1m b\u1ee5i, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean v\u1ec7 sinh<\/p>\n<h2><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5001 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1227\" height=\"920\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-5.jpg 1227w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-5-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-5-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-5-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-5-510x382.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1227px) 100vw, 1227px\" title=\"\"><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5002 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1227\" height=\"920\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-6.jpg 1227w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-6-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-6-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-6-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-6-510x382.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1227px) 100vw, 1227px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000080; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif;\"><strong>2.2. R\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng &#8211; R\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n l\u01b0\u1edbi:<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>R\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n n\u00e0y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c khu v\u1ef1c qu\u00e1n cafe, nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng, bar, ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch&#8230;c\u00e1c khu v\u1ef1c c\u1ea7n \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng. R\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3n 70% \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng chi\u1ebfu qua t\u1ea5m m\u00e0n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, b\u00ean trong ph\u00f2ng nh\u00ecn ra ngo\u00e0i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y nh\u01b0ng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o trong kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n l\u01b0\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; R\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n l\u01b0\u1edbi mang v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng th\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00f9ng trong trang tr\u00ed.<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i khi k\u00e9o r\u00e8m xu\u1ed1ng.<\/p>\n<p>H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n l\u01b0\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t, c\u1ea3n tia UV \u00a0\u00edt h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5003 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1227\" height=\"920\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-7.jpg 1227w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-7-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-7-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-7-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/rem-cuon-chong-nang-tai-cau-giay-7-510x382.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1227px) 100vw, 1227px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><strong>Xem th\u00eam<\/strong>:\u00a0<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"> \u00a0<span style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-vai-hai-lop\/\">Nh\u1eefng M\u1eabu R\u00e8m V\u1ea3i Hai L\u1edbp \u0110\u1eb9p Nh\u1ea5t 2020<\/a><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">\u00a0\u00a0<a style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/huong-dan-cach-chon-rem-chung-cu-sang-trong\/\">H\u01b0\u1edbng D\u1eabn C\u00